v1.1
  - Fix overlay: MCP2518FD (not MCP2515) on SPI0 CE1 / GPIO7 (not CE0 / GPIO8)
  - Fix overlay: 20 MHz oscillator (not 16 MHz)
  - Add optional NMEA 2000 dbus bridge (MacArthurN2K service / dbus_n2k.py)
    Workaround for CAN transceiver TX path issues that prevent vecan-dbus
    from completing address claiming. Ships disabled; enable via setup prompt.
    Currently decodes PGN 127505 (Fluid Level) → com.victronenergy.tank.

v1.0
  Initial release.
  - MCP2518FD CAN controller overlay for NMEA2000 on SPI0 CE1 / GPIO25 IRQ
  - GPIO overlay configuring GPIO21 (SHUTDOWN_REQ, pull-up input) and
    GPIO26 (DCDC_EN, output)
  - Shutdown monitor daemon: holds GPIO26 HIGH to keep DC-DC converter
    enabled, drives GPIO26 LOW after graceful shutdown
  - udev rule to bring up can0 at 250 kbps for NMEA2000
  - SetupHelper-compatible setup/uninstall script
